// "Casting flash of light inside consecrated ground makes you radiate holy energy, exploding in a
// small radius around you, dealing X damage to nearby enemies" (Mechanics, epic, unique). Installs
// the "flash_of_light_consecrated_radiate" ActiveHooks flag; execute_ready_abilities checks it
// AND `PlayerZonePresence::is_inside("consecrated_ground")` at cast start, baking the result into
// Channeling.consecrated_radiate_damage.
(
    id: "flash_of_light_consecrated_radiate_epic",
    display_name: "Hallowed Blast",
    ability_scope: Some("flash_of_light"),
    rarity: Epic,
    uniqueness: Exclusive,
    effect: Behavior("flash_of_light_consecrated_radiate"),
)
